{"tid":862094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ CLS香港 ] 承認明日大嶼計劃洗好多錢　陳茂波稱或考慮發債籌旗","createTime":"2018-10-14T15:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T11:48:05.000Z","uid":1221,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"747b87a11523f8efa47026f56bfec50008e88a7d","tid":862094,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T15:12:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://passiontimes.hk/uploads/images/201810/F96A7F9D0B0E45499998ED659692B6C2_O.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F201810%2FF96A7F9D0B0E45499998ED659692B6C2_O.JPG&h=f2104109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《施政報告》提出的「明日大嶼」計劃，坊間估計隨時要花上近萬億資金，被指是掏空庫房的超級大白象。財政司司長陳茂波今日（10月14日）出席單車節活動之後，指雖然發展局仍未仔細預算開支，但承認項目會「洗好多錢」。 <br />\n<br />\n陳茂波表示，本港現時財政狀況非常健康，有過萬億元儲備，而填海項目難免動用一部分儲備，至於如何籌儲費用，則有很多變數，他指項目涉及房屋，能夠透過賣地及出售津助房屋，賺取收入，此外，交通項目上蓋亦可以發展，收回地價補貼建築和營運費開支。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波又提到過去金融風暴的時候，也嘗試將五隧一橋來舉債，他指如果本身是好項目、有回報率，如果考慮過認為合適，認為發債是其中一個方法，亦令市民大眾有穩定的投資工具。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/19ZUDO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2F19ZUDO.gif&h=c545780c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f588e9bb6378e6540ea9cd92c6d3c4df8740e7e7","tid":862094,"uid":61280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T15:14:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>上次機管焗個招借D兒想常態化？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n庫房明有錢但就繞過正正經經Legco批錢，情願出街借明醒支那行盲賺高息，又搵鳩納稅人笨柒！！！！</span></span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263da0a129ce131fa9b1166435d34c9ec4538cb4","tid":862094,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T15:14:55.000Z","msg":"<